view.name: Donor and Government funded projects map 2013 - 2015
view.description: This dataset visualizes the summarized distribution of Donor and Government funded Projects across the Country. Together with the location information on projects the dataset contains descriptive information about the project, the total financial estimates and the average estimated costs per year based on the duration of the project. Some Usage notes: Due to the limited detail of financial data do not calculate totals or add any fields together..
